ca.uqac.lif.cep.SingleProcessor

  • Packages that use SingleProcessor 
    Package Description
    ca.uqac.lif.cep
    Elementary classes defining all the basic concepts of event stream processing.
    ca.uqac.lif.cep.eml.numbers  
    ca.uqac.lif.cep.eml.tuples
    Processors and functions for event traces made of tuples of name-value pairs.
    ca.uqac.lif.cep.epl
    Processors to manipulate traces of generic events.
    ca.uqac.lif.cep.gnuplot
    Processors for generating realtime graphs with the help of Gnuplot.
    ca.uqac.lif.cep.input
    Processors to handle conversions to and from various data formats.
    ca.uqac.lif.cep.io
    Processors to handle input and output of data from external sources, such as files and pipes.
    ca.uqac.lif.cep.ltl
    Processors to express complex patterns over sequences of events with Linear Temporal Logic.
    ca.uqac.lif.cep.signal
    Signal processing functionalities: peak detection, threshold, etc.
